                                <p>I am pleased to invite you all to the first African Science Frontiers Initiatives (ASFI) conference and boot camp. The conference will be an annual event that brings African researchers, scientists, and stakeholders together to present, network, and learn. It will be an opportunity for collaboration, and cooperation, and showcase the latest African research. The conference will be multidisciplinary and interdisciplinary where experts and interested scholars from various African countries and diaspora and from different fields will meet and so have enriching discussions aiming to advance scientific research and development of Africa. </p>
                                <p>This maiden ASFI conference and boot camp will be a place for capacity building and gathering senior & junior African scholars to meet, work together, and have inspiration through workshops, games, quizzes & competitions.  It is important to say that the conference and boot camp encourages participation from all scientific fields, and all career levels. Students are also welcomed to attend, present, and participate in discussions so they can exchange and gain new knowledge, advance their careers, gain new skills and be active contributors for Africa’s scientific development.</p>
                                <p>ASFI conference and boot camp 2023 will take place from 28th to 30th November 2023 online. Save the date and do not miss the opportunity to attend this event and be engaged with African scholars.</p>
